{"tid":635970,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】女模拍攝寫真走光被瘋傳　 疑似 CCTV 影像相流出","createTime":"2018-04-20T12:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T06:42:14.000Z","uid":29540,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9825f1eeba19489e0e9045b8739d464c6daa80","tid":635970,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:43:04.000Z","msg":"講到本地女模，論到作風大膽，喺網上略有名氣，真係無乜幾多個。多年來都被討論區留意，自2015年起多次上報。 佢不時都喺IG同Facebook上登上大膽照，上晒豬肉枱，落泳池影大膽照，仲有車房洗車圖集，一直都幾多曝光，2016年仲有套電影香港大師添。講緊嘅就係Colanda，近日網上流傳佢拍攝一輯寫真時，不慎流出走光照。"},{"pid":"ca3775f6b4db029448dd020329b671c8d8955b7a","tid":635970,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37221c6fd6e400bfe48888ea0eb6b21c3d8727f3","tid":635970,"uid":139687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"瘋傳.....連登"},{"pid":"50fd59fa6a6eddd4fd8d90fcbdee6ff596b1e255","tid":635970,"uid":116330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:45:12.000Z","msg":"你老母俾我瘋傳緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e6e1e808c51ad22014e3a3c5811152d6c6fd45","tid":635970,"uid":39256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"又係無連登份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23092f27c625395b8944e6b1e7e69eef15382a6d","tid":635970,"uid":60787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"網絡孤島-連登"},{"pid":"066bdf43c62ed1b8f7a817a21ee3254785ea1198","tid":635970,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"「瘋傳」呢句蝗語冇人識走去屌？<br />\n<br />\n由此可見連登仔只識跟風冇獨立思維"},{"pid":"ffbe23ea130fd8dd43454397eff38e7a4fd6509b","tid":635970,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"連登又無份<img src=\"/as